{"tid":1194673,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"華為最新旗艦Mate 30將如常上市，改用鴻蒙系統(Oak OS)取代Android","createTime":"2019-06-09T11:00:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T05:57:23.000Z","uid":155095,"like":29,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"89731f88848279248cd5a87b1c5d92e5ab5662a4","tid":1194673,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T11:00:36.000Z","msg":"<strong>Mate 30 上市計劃無阻   華為將改用鴻蒙上陣</strong><br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4546/213245/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4546%2F213245%2F1%2F&d=QsQvn9KnS4zrnMXWGBKJeCPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=9d003537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4546/213245/1/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2019-06/09/213245/uniqlo_1_cdc7fe9aa798f2dd71e505aa0711d860.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2019-06%2F09%2F213245%2Funiqlo_1_cdc7fe9aa798f2dd71e505aa0711d860.jpg&h=8f8a6024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日前有消息指華為自家系統的中文名字會叫做「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鴻蒙</span></strong>」，而英文則會以 <strong>Ark OS</strong> 命名，不過日前大陸的環球時報在官方 Twitter 發帖，指華為新系統的名字最後定案為 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Oak OS</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2019-06/09/213245/uniqlo_1_8fe3f540dd8fa020720004fd736313d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2019-06%2F09%2F213245%2Funiqlo_1_8fe3f540dd8fa020720004fd736313d0.jpg&h=0f0b9c41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環球時報又透露系統會在 <span style=\"color: red;\">8 月或 9 月推出</span>，並引述消息人士指日期會和 <strong>Mate 30</strong> 系列發表脗合，意味著這旗艦系列可能會使用自家「鴻蒙」系統，令新機上市不受美國的禁令影響。"},{"pid":"2e8c15e8abb303a58a3bcb4f7767bc161953c359","tid":1194673,"uid":156511,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T11:01:57.000Z","msg":"蒙卵系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff811611c49a6111af611ae69a7ff1946a44074","tid":1194673,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T11:02:25.000Z","msg":"noted with thanks"},{"pid":"8cdc70eaa3dadb9caf2e077a40a06106ea338825","tid":1194673,"uid":1327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T11:05:03.000Z","msg":"咪又係aosp"},{"pid":"a0c6c4105bc70d0aa509569f30e53b2d8eb30e60","tid":1194673,"uid":12021,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T11:07:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7dbb0fe6d98530b4320ab580f4d226447b046b87","tid":1194673,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T11:09:55.000Z","msg":"咁快上得到即係都係AOSP底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4b9b0c19a5ea878ab60ed438381faddfd4cbb5","tid":1194673,"uid":189358,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T11:12:06.000Z","msg":"買定包花生<br />\n睇下有幾好賣？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cddaaabed0578cd63d70e18d8b29f5f2c245ec11","tid":1194673,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T11:14:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">中文名字會叫做「鴻蒙」，而英文則會以 Ark OS 命名</span><br />\n<br />\nHomo 呃OS"},{"pid":"fbb426ffda6e2d9928c00890632fdfd813a4e6a9","tid":1194673,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T13:11:44.000Z","msg":"白牌 Aosp就 apsp啦，好懵os <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af264f245929a637b7f629e7e35e3c0d0809e69b","tid":1194673,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi